Para ser lembrado

234
00:14:40,129 --> 00:14:42,048
Se der

235
00:14:42,131 --> 00:14:46,719
Em uma ocasião qualquer

236
00:14:46,803 --> 00:14:48,805
Se eu sair

237
00:14:50,306 --> 00:14:53,935
Se eu puder

238
00:14:53,976 --> 00:14:55,937
Quero ir

239
00:14:55,978 --> 00:14:58,064
Aonde

240
